Content.Text:
<NAME_MOB_FRANCISKA>
I'm busy right now! I need to feed my cats! Get
out of my way!

<NAME_MOB_FRANCISKA>
Ah, sheesh! I thought I'd need this thing I just
bought, but it turned out to be a waste of
money.

<NAME_MOB_FRANCISKA>
Why in the world did I buy something like this?
How am I even going to get it all the way home?

<NAME_MOB_FRANCISKA>
I gotta go home and feed my cats!

<NAME_MOB_FRANCISKA>
What do you want? I'm in a hurry. Leave me
alone!

<NAME_MOB_FRANCISKA>
This costs HOW much?! Come on, I came all
this way just to shop here. Help me out, will
you?

<NAME_MOB_FRANCISKA>
Why is everyone in this town so easygoing?! Are
they even trying?!

<NAME_MOB_FRANCISKA>
I have a lot of cats, and cat food gets expensive.
That's why I'm here!

<NAME_MOB_FRANCISKA>
You know, it's nice that cat food's cheaper now,
but there're always so many people around!
They're so annoying!

<NAME_MOB_FRANCISKA>
Now my cats refuse to eat anything except the
food I buy them here. They're so selfish!
